If the Rebellion is to be crushed, you must seek out and destroy their headquarters.  In addition, the Emperor has ordered that the Rebel leaders, Senator Mon Mothma and Luke Skywalker, must be captured. If you chose 'Headquarters Only Victory', you need only destroy the Rebel headquarters. At the same time, the Rebels will be attempting to capture the Emperor and Lord Vader as well as invade the Imperial capital at Coruscant. Use the Objectives window from my right click menu to see how the campaign is progressing.